Package Proyecto1.DatosParty.Boxes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Box
    This class is the base for all the other boxes.
    GreenBox
    Class of implementing the green box, it has the hability to give 10 coins to a player, when placed on it.
    IntersectionBox
    Class of implementing the intersection box, it has no events asociated, this box is the secret key to find the possible ways on the table, it stores inside a phase instance and an exit point.
    RedBox
    Class of implementing the red box, it has the hability to take 10 coins from a player, when placed on it.
    WhiteBox
    Class of implementing the white box, it has no capacity to interact with the player.
    YellowBox
    Class of implementing the green box, it has the capacity to trigger an event from the event stack.
